It would fit in a cart with two program (PRG) banks (2x 8KB). Then you would have plenty of space for the code that display the text.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=504">Jaffe</a> — Tue May 16, 2006 12:30 pm</p><hr />
